text: Lynique Beneke (née Prinsloo; born 30 March 1991) is a South African athlete specialising in the long jump. She represented her country at the 2013 World Championships without qualifying for the final. Her personal best in the event is 6.81 metres (-1.2 m/s) set in Stellenbosch in 2013.
